{
  "root": {
    "children": [
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "For this week’s Switch Kickstarter Project of the Week, we will be looking at COWCAT's ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "BROK the InvestiGator",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". The game is slated to release in December 2021 on PC (via Steam and gog.com), PS4, PS5, Xbox and Nintendo Switch.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Here's the overview:",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "BROK the InvestiGator blends a Classic Adventure (puzzles, inventory, narrative...) with elements from Beat 'em Ups and RPGs!",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "What?! How does that even work?!",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "At any time, with the press of a button or mouse wheel scroll, you can switch between adventure and action mode.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The whole game - story, characters, gameplay - everything has been built around this premise that you can progress in various ways. Will you choose to solve mysteries with your brain, or will you break your way through?   ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The game spans over 6 long chapters for 15 to 20 hours of gameplay on your first playthrough. (The prologue contains the first chapter)",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Not an estimate - that's the actual time it took my early testers to finish it!",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "As you may notice, the characters and story are inspired by cartoons from the 80's/early 90's - but with a darker spin.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Past events lead to this corrupted world where a small number of privileged citizens named \"Drumers\" live under a dome, while others are forced to endure the threats of polluted slums.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Brok, former boxer turned detective after the death of his wife, was forced to leave the dome to take care of her son Graff. Always on the run, Brok can barely make ends meet and never has much time for him. Graff aspires to become a \"Drumer\" again - but trials on his path push him back...",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Little do they know that bigger threats are upcoming - which may be linked to their own past.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "How will they face them?... That's up to you!",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "quote",
        "version": 1
      },
